Neural Networks. 

Explanation: The paper discusses the capabilities of Single Layer Recurrent Neural Networks (SLRNNs) with hard-limiting neurons, and compares the representational power of first-order and second-order SLRNNs. The paper also discusses how augmented first-order SLRNNs can be used to efficiently implement finite-state recognizers using state-splitting. Therefore, the paper primarily belongs to the sub-category of Neural Networks in AI.
